<br />
<br />tilex = (xpos+Xscroll)/8
<br />tiley = (xpos+Yscroll)/8
<br />
<br />Huh? why would that be the formula? Can I have a more newbie friendly explanation? I'm not implying that I'm a newbie, I'm just asking for a simpler explanation.</div>

