						<div class="postbody">blargg is right. Draw it down on paper. It alway helps me too. Draw the grid of tiles, draw your player over it in different positions and try to find your formula from that. We can't give you the exact formulas, we don't know your game. We don't know the size of your map, the size of your sprites, any of that. We can only help you with the concepts, give you examples and all, but it is up to you to convert to your specific needs.</div>

